| File              | What it does                                          |
| ----------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| **DriverManager** | Stores the browser (WebDriver) so everyone can use it |
| **DriverFactory** | Creates the browser (Chrome, Firefox, etc.)           |
| **BaseTest**      | Starts and closes the browser for every test          |
| **BasePage**      | Common methods for all pages (click, type, wait)      |


| ---------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| **ConfigLoader** | Reads values from `.properties` files |
| **Config**       | Gives those values to your code       |


| ------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| **HeaderComponent** | Handles top part of the site (logo, search, cart, login)  |

                                       |
| ---------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| **CheckoutPage** | Main checkout screen (continue, place order, summary) |
| **AddressPage**  | Enter/select shipping address                         |
| **PaymentPage**  | Enter payment details and pay                         |

                                                           |
| --------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Waits**       | All waiting logic (wait for element, wait for click, wait for visible) |
| **ActionsUtil** | Mouse/keyboard actions (hover, drag, scroll, double click)             |
| **Screenshots** | Takes screenshots on demand or on failure                              |
| **AllureAttachments** | Attaches screenshots/logs to Allure report                       |

                              |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| **TestListener** | Listens to test events (start, pass, fail) |
